'''limestone'''
#{{mineralogy}} An abundant [[rock]] of [[marine]] and fresh-water [[sediment]]s; primarily composed of [[calcite]] (CaCO<sub>3</sub>); it occurs in a variety of forms, both [[crystal]]line and [[amorphous]].  
